  <p>The basis of the the system of fear and silos, is exchange.</p>
  <p>Don't have anything to trade? Have no interest in doing a task? Well then you're going to starve.</p>
  <p>I will only give you something, if I get something of equal value in return.</p>
  <p>That is the habit that we need to break; one interaction at a time.</p>
